This code accepts a string of 1 letter protein codes, and translates them to 3 letter codes

create screen
    create text box for input
    create button to translate
    create label to display output
    when button is clicked
        get input
        for each letter in input
            make letter upper case
            if letter not in dictionary
                display error message
                exit
            translate letter
            add translated letter to output
        display output
